{"word":"ἀναρπαστός","slug":"ἀναρπαστός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναρπαστός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀναρπάζω'><el>ἀναρπάζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>snatched up, carried off</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>carried up the country</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> into Central Asia, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}